comments: She is a great professor. She was my lab professor.It is a hard class, but she makes it easy.Her tests are easy.She is great.Five exams,drop the lowest grades,tests are not a burden. Got an A in the lab and lecture. Overall great professor....

she is the most loved professor ever. love her class, and yes i am a very brilliant student so passing was not an issue, she break things down and make it easy for u. she tries her best not to overwhelm u on test. studying is a must in her class. she will tell u what u need to study and does not just read from text book. take her

Good professor. AHS131 is a very hard class. she tries not to overwhelm you with too much info which is good. I had her for lecture, she gives a couple of extra credits that count towards the tests (Sometimes you have to ask for it). She follows the book. if you DONT GET BEHIND ON THE MATERIAL, STUDY UR CLASS NOTES & BOOK EVERYDAY you will do fine.

very hard class. i dropped it but i still learned alot. she is a really good professor - i did like the class. attendance is not mandatory, but you won\'t pass unless you show up! i thought she dressed nice!
She is a really good teacher. She does tell you what will be in the exam. But you must attend class, also she dropped the lowest grade in lab. Awesome! Just be prepared for her "outfits" .

Excellent, test are quite difficult. She understand students. help with outlines which helps to reinforce the notes she gives in class and what you read from the book. TAKE A CLASS WITH HER AND STUDY AND YOU WILL DO GREAT!!

Very difficulty course, that she made seem easy. Really have to study, but can do very well. The tests are hard, but if you study you will do well. She is readily available to help with questions. I really liked the class.

good professor. she teaches from the textbook in order of the textbook which makes it extremely helpful when studing. she provides useful notes via email and she is willing to answer any questions and concerns
